name: Beal 16mm Nylon Tubular Webbing
description: Narrower gauge tubular webbing for making custom-length, skinnier slings with reasonable strength. This is appropriate for climbing applications that don't require the strength of a pre-sewn sling.This product is sold by the metre.Made of nylon.16mm width.Strength is approximately 13kN static (1350kg).Note: tying a knot in webbing reduces strength and does not meet the CE sling standard of 22kN, which is achievable with pre-sewn slings.
